86
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:55,350
我们一起工作  我刚提拔了她
We're working together. I just promoted her.

87
00:02:55,350 --> 00:02:57,390
这更多是借口不是理由  不是吗
That's more an excuse than a reason, isn't it?

88
00:02:57,390 --> 00:02:59,300
我不想在没有问题时制造问题
I don't want to create a problem when there isn't one.

89
00:02:59,330 --> 00:03:00,630
谁说非得有问题了
And who says there has to be one?

90
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,780
不非得有  但是...
There doesn't have to be one, but--

91
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:05,650
