Harvey, first of all, you may be underestimating her.

92
00:03:05,650 --> 00:03:07,290
-唐娜已经是个大姑娘了  -宝拉...
- I mean, Donna's a big girl. - Paula--

93
00:03:07,290 --> 00:03:08,730
