00:05:44,130 --> 00:05:45,700
那天  我对你说那些话时
The other day when I said those things to you

161
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:47,350
关于休假的事
about taking time off, I mean,

162
00:05:47,350 --> 00:05:48,620
